headline: REG- A Diversified Shopping Center REIT with a Solid Yield
summary: Regency Centers Corp. (REG) is an owner, operator, and developer of shopping centers located in suburban areas with strong demographics. Major markets are in geographic areas located in states throughout the Northeast, Mid-Atlantic, Southeast, and the Midwest, highlights Martin Fridson, editor of Forbes/Fridson Income Securities Investor.
